messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 6/3/03 6:49:29 PM Eastern Daylight Time, KathrynJB@...
writes:


> Where in the Keys are you? My parents used to live on Cudjoe, and they
> owned
> small grocery stores on Cudjoe and at one time, Key West. Cool place :)
>

Big Coppitt... MM 10. It was a cool place to live for about the first 6
months... now it's just kind of weird. EVERYTHING is so expensive. However, June
is "free locals month" so a lot of the museums and stuff are free right now.
I need to get out and do something with these kids besides fish and swim
(although we do enjoy those things : ) ~Kris
